properties.title: The Civil Wars [260/365]
properties.description: taylor anne photography posted a photo: Thanks to my best friend Kellie I have found another band to obsess over. If you haven't listened to The Civil Wars yet then I beg you to! They are wonderful! This is the best shot I got at their show because there was this extremely tall douche bag in front of me and I could barely see. It was awful! But no matter that I still had fun because these two are extremely talented musicians!

properties.title: Michael Angarano [261/365]
properties.description: taylor anne photography posted a photo: Yes we got to meet Will Stronghold too. We got invited to see the US premiere of his new movie Ceremony and we met him on the way in. He was incredibly nice and extremely down to earth and we wanted to bad to just invite him out or something but we were too nervous so we didn't. Whatevs we still got a picture with him and had a good conversation.
